{"tid":1923686,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"又有手足認罪）旺角私了8/12手足認罪還押候判","createTime":"2020-03-13T08:15:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T11:59:26.000Z","uid":333488,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb0028126ad815a67a12b2d6a2e31160ca7023f","tid":1923686,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"去年12.8大遊行後的翌日凌晨，大批市民在旺角一帶聚集及堵路，其間有男子疑因政見問題，於街頭遭「私了」昏迷倒地。警方接報，翻看閉路電視片段，識別疑犯衣著後在附近拘捕一名巴基斯坦裔男生，男生承認曾以棍打及踢對方，他今在裁判法院承認襲擊傷人罪，須還柙候判。被告Hamaad Mahmood（18歲）持香港身份證，他承認於去年12月9日在旺角西洋菜南街與山東街交界，襲擊男子陳大鵬，對陳大鵬造成身體傷害。據控方指，陳事後頭部腫瘀，腳有擦傷。主任裁判官羅德泉索閱被告勞教、教導所、心理專家及背景報告，將被告還柙至本月27日判刑。辯方求情時呈上被告校長及社工求情信，指被告樂於助人，對所犯錯誤已深感後悔，望能索閱感化報告才判刑。<br />\n<br />\n黑警打人呢？dllm"},{"pid":"77607c1c6769a41913759f508bc8dee7e09e124d","tid":1923686,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:45:43.000Z","msg":"又係依個狗官<br />\n<br />\n西九裁判法庭新案件 喧嘩都要宵禁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1923630\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1923630</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2fe2efd82593977343e0d9e94df020f82479f4b4","tid":1923686,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:47:51.000Z","msg":"南亞手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTqXb0P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTqXb0P.gif&h=31e53dd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1c888367f0926813d4c9ee6b677cfe33c982a4d","tid":1923686,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T08:49:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67510b093a44b0f00204d6a3915d25df73b96d6f","tid":1923686,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-13T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norma